WEBVTT

00:02.200 --> 00:04.476
[♪♪♪]

00:04.680 --> 00:07.514
ANNOUNCER:
<i>This is the story of two sisters:</i>

00:07.760 --> 00:11.470
<i>Jessica Tate and Mary Campbell.</i>

00:11.720 --> 00:15.953
<i>Jessica lives in a neighbourhood</i>
<i>known as rich.</i>

00:16.160 --> 00:17.753
<i>Jessica likes life.</i>

00:17.960 --> 00:20.953
<i>The only thing about life</i>
<i>she would change, if she could,</i>

00:21.160 --> 00:23.595
<i>is that she would set it</i>
<i>all to music.</i>

00:25.000 --> 00:28.676
<i>The Tates have more secrets</i>
<i>than they do money.</i>

00:31.320 --> 00:34.518
<i>We're approaching</i>
<i>Mary Campbell's house.</i>

00:36.280 --> 00:37.839
<i>Mary, too, likes life.</i>

00:38.040 --> 00:41.875
<i>Unfortunately, life doesn't seem</i>
<i>to be too crazy about her.</i>

00:42.080 --> 00:46.791
<i>As you can see, the Campbells</i>
<i>don't have nearly as much money</i>
<i>as the Tates.</i>

00:47.560 --> 00:51.270
<i>They do, however,</i>
<i>have as many secrets.</i>

00:55.080 --> 00:57.117
<i>In last week's episode of</i> Soap

00:57.360 --> 00:59.317
<i>Mary realises that Jessica</i>
<i>and Corinne</i>

00:59.520 --> 01:02.831
<i>are playing something other</i>
<i>than tennis with Peter, the tennis pro.</i>

01:03.080 --> 01:04.833
<i>Neither Jessica nor Corinne</i>
<i>realise</i>

01:05.080 --> 01:07.959
<i>that they both are engaged</i>
<i>in a game of mixed doubles.</i>

01:08.160 --> 01:10.391
<i>Jessica is so overwhelmed</i>
<i>with guilt</i>

01:10.600 --> 01:13.195
<i>she attempts to confess</i>
<i>her affair to Chester.</i>

01:13.400 --> 01:14.834
<i>But Chester isn't listening,</i>

01:15.040 --> 01:19.239
<i>because he's so overwhelmed by his</i>
<i>secretary Claire's blackmail attempts.</i>

01:19.480 --> 01:22.314
<i>Meanwhile at the Campbells,</i>
<i>Mary has threatened to move out</i>

01:22.520 --> 01:24.671
<i>unless Burt and Danny</i>
<i>try to get along.</i>

01:24.920 --> 01:26.798
<i>Getting along with</i>
<i>his stepfather, Burt,</i>

01:27.000 --> 01:28.912
<i>becomes even more difficult</i>
<i>for Danny</i>

01:29.120 --> 01:32.591
<i>once the Godfather tells him Burt</i>
<i>was the man who killed his father.</i>

01:32.840 --> 01:35.958
<i>Since the Mob will kill Danny</i>
<i>if he doesn't kill Burt,</i>

01:36.200 --> 01:39.591
<i>Danny realises trying to please</i>
<i>his mother will be a problem.</i>

01:39.800 --> 01:41.598
<i>But Mary's problems</i>
<i>don't end there,</i>

01:41.800 --> 01:44.679
<i>since her other son, Jodie,</i>
<i>is about to become her daughter.</i>

01:44.880 --> 01:45.880
<i>Confused?</i>

01:46.040 --> 01:50.159
<i>You won't be after</i>
<i>this week's episode of</i> Soap.

